'''Lucasfilm Animation Singapore''', a division of [[Lucasfilm]] that opened on [[October 27]], [[2005]].<ref name="This Week Carpet">{{ThisWeek|dTR7q_0_YOQ|The Mandalorian Virtual Red Carpet Premiere, What Scares the Jedi, and More!}}</ref> It is a digital animation studio that produces Lucasfilm's digital animated content for films, games and television. Lucasfilm Animation Singapore is responsible for the creation of the animated series ''[[Star Wars: The Clone Wars]]'' in conjunction with [[Lucasfilm Animation]]. Lucasfilm Animation Singapore also developed two [[Star Wars video games|video game]]s based on ''The Clone Wars''.

